                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;"><b>Gemini (May 21 - June 20):</b></p>
                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">Represented by the Twins, Geminis are characterized by their dual nature, adaptability, and intellectual curiosity. They excel in communication, love to socialize, and are adept at seeing multiple perspectives.</p>
                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;"><b>Cancer (June 21 - July 22):</b></p>
                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">Cancerians, symbolized by the Crab, are nurturing, intuitive, and deeply empathetic individuals. They prioritize emotional connections, family bonds, and creating safe havens where they can express their vulnerability.</p>
                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;"><b>Leo (July 23 - August 22):</b></p>
                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">Leos, symbolized by the Lion, are natural-born leaders, radiating confidence, charisma, and warmth. They thrive in the spotlight, enjoy being admired, and possess a generous spirit that uplifts those around them.</p>
