                <p class="as_font14 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;">Scorpios are intense, passionate, and mysterious individuals, symbolized by the Scorpion. They possess a deep emotional depth, resilience, and a magnetic allure that draws others to them.</p>
